OL,3,CKidnappers who put victim through
OL,4,C'terrifying ordeal' jailed for 28 years
OL,6,FThree men who kidnapped a man and
OL,7,Fthreatened him with a knife have been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FDean Meaker, 58, Hassan Noor, 31, and
OL,11,FLee Ingleheart, 41 held their victim
OL,12,Fagainst his will in a bid to find out
OL,13,Finformation about one of his relatives.
OL,15,FThe court heard how the three men
OL,16,Fplotted to kidnap the 43-year-old from
OL,17,Fhis home in Thornbury on October 20
OL,18,F2022.
