OL,3,CKidnappers who put victim through
OL,4,C'terrifying ordeal' jailed for 28 years
OL,6,FThey used one of his acquaintances to
OL,7,Farrange a meeting at his home at
OL,8,Faround 4pm and when he answered the
OL,9,Fdoor they went inside, subjecting him
OL,10,Fto threats and violence.
OL,12,FThey led him to a Ford Transit van,
OL,13,Fbefore taking him to another property
OL,14,Fin the Stoke Park area, where he was
OL,15,Fheld against his will and subjected to
OL,16,Ffurther assaults and threats.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
