OL,6,FHe managed to escape the property when
OL,7,Ftwo of the defendants left to buy
OL,8,Fdrugs, hiding in a nearby street and
OL,9,Fseeking help from a member of the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,FA member of the public had called Avon
OL,13,Fand Somerset Police after witnessing
OL,14,FIngleheart near the Thornbury address
OL,15,Fwith a large knife.
OL,17,FArmed officers were deployed in search
OL,18,Fof the Ford Transit van and it was
OL,19,Fstopped in east Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
