OL,6,FVan, knuckle duster and knives seized
OL,7,Fby police
OL,9,FNoor and Meaker were arrested at
OL,10,Faround 7.40pm and officers seized
OL,11,Fweapons from the van, including a
OL,12,Fknuckle duster and knives.
OL,14,FOfficers also attended the property in
OL,15,FStoke Park, where Ingleheart was
OL,16,Farrested at 8.45pm. When officers
OL,17,Fsearched the property, they found a
OL,18,Fknife that had been used to threaten
OL,19,Fthe victim.
