OL,4,C'terrifying ordeal' jailed for 28 years
OL,6,FIngleheart, of no fixed address, was
OL,7,Fsentenced to nine years and nine
OL,8,Fmonths with an additional four years
OL,9,Fon licence when he's released from
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FTrio sentenced to more than 28 years
OL,13,Fin prison
OL,15,FNoor, of Midland Street, Bristol, was
OL,16,Fsentenced to nine years in jail, and
OL,17,FMeaker, of Westward Road, Bristol, was
OL,18,Fsentenced to nine years' imprisonment,
OL,19,Fas well as a further six months for an
OL,20,Funrelated burglary.
