OL,6,FThe last of the sentencing hearings
OL,7,Fwas held at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,8,FDecember 17.
OL,10,FInvestigating officer Det Con Carl
OL,11,FSpicer said: "The victim in this case
OL,12,Fwent through a terrifying ordeal at
OL,13,Fthe hands of these three criminals,
OL,14,Fwho showed an extremely concerning
OL,15,Fpropensity for violence, as well as
OL,16,Fbeing in possession of some fearsome
OL,17,Fweapons.
