OL,3,CKidnappers who put victim through
OL,4,C'terrifying ordeal' jailed for 28 years
OL,6,F"He's shown immense bravery in telling
OL,7,Fthe police what happened to him and we
OL,8,Fhope he continues to recover from this
OL,9,Fhorrible experience.
OL,11,F"We want to thank the members of the
OL,12,Fpublic who called police with vital
OL,13,Finformation ` their actions ensured
OL,14,Farmed officers were deployed and able
OL,15,Fto swiftly arrest those responsible.
OL,17,F"This has been a challenging
OL,18,Finvestigation which has thankfully
OL,19,Fresulted in these dangerous offenders
OL,20,Fbeing removed from the streets for a
OL,21,Fsignificant amount of time."
